r.c.H(0,A.aw(["en_US",A.aw(["about_me","I am a Software Engineer with over 12 years of experience specializing in Python backend development, microservices, and API design. I have more than 8 years of hands-on Python experience building robust platforms, automation frameworks, and production-grade systems.\n\nCurrently, I focus on developing automation and production pipeline tools for Digital Content Creation (DCC) environments. I have worked both within organizations and on independent projects, delivering workflow-oriented solutions that are actively used in real production. I am passionate about turning complex technical processes into stable, well-tested systems that teams can rely on.",p,"I started programming in 2007 working with PIC microcontrollers using Assembler and C. Later, I completed tertiary studies in Systems Analysis and Programming, strengthening my skills in Java and Python.\n\nOver time, I transitioned into backend engineering, focusing on Python microservices, API design, automation frameworks, and production pipeline systems. Today, I work primarily with Python for backend development and Flutter for selected mobile applications, while continuously exploring new technologies such as Rust.",o,"Throughout my career I have developed strong communication, problem-solving, and collaboration skills. I have worked in roles ranging from employee to entrepreneur and technical lead, which helped me strengthen teamwork, conflict resolution, and leadership capabilities in complex technical environments.","sysadmin_text","My experience with system administration began in 2007 and expanded through professional work configuring servers, RAID systems, and networking infrastructure. Over time I gained hands-on experience with Linux, Windows Server, virtualization, networking, Kubernetes clusters, and Google Cloud services, giving me a solid understanding of production infrastructure and deployment workflows.","full_stack_text","Although I work across the full stack when required, my main contribution is on backend platforms and automation systems that power production workflows, including Python-based services, configuration validation tools, environment builders, and pipeline integrations used in real-world DCC production.","frontend_text","My frontend experience is strongly tied to production needs. I have developed Flutter mobile applications such as Dockaboat and CareCart, implementing complex features like payment systems with Stripe, real-time integrations, authentication, and data synchronization, always ensuring clean communication with backend services.","backend_text","My core expertise lies in building Python backend platforms and microservice-based systems. I design and implement REST and GraphQL APIs, asynchronous services, WebSocket-based real-time communication layers, configuration validation tooling, and automation frameworks that are actively used in production environments.","deployment_text","I have hands-on experience deploying and maintaining production systems, including Docker-based services, CI/CD pipelines, environment provisioning tools, and monitoring workflows. My work ensures that backend platforms, pipeline tools, and mobile applications can be reliably built, deployed, and updated across development and production environments.","electronic_text","My interest in electronics started in childhood and later expanded into embedded systems, CNC development, and hardware\u2013software integration projects using microcontrollers and MicroPython.","about_me_title","Personal Information","about","About Me","_age","Age: ","_profession","Profession: ","_nationality","Nationality: ","_current_residence","City of Residence: ","age"," %age years.","profession","Python Backend & Automation Platforms","nationality","Argentinian.","current_residence","Bariloche, R\xedo Negro, Argentina","programming","Programming","electronic","Electronic","sysadmin","Systems Administrator","soft_skills","Soft Skills","languages","Languages","queryLanguages","Query Languages","paradigms","Paradigms","objectOriented","Object Oriented (OOP)","concurrent","Concurrent","reactive","Reactive","parallel","Parallel","functional","Functional","declarative","Declarative","serviceOriented","Service Oriented","_about_me","About Me","_knowledge","Skills","_experience","Experience","_projects","Projects","_contact","Contact","full_stack_developer","Backend & Automation Engineer","frontend","Frontend","backend","Backend","deployment_management","Deployment Management","structure_planning","Structure Planning","database_design","Database Design","security_implementation","Security Implementation","ux","User experience","ui","User interface","performance","Performance","deployment_structure","Deployment Structure","ci","Continuous Integration","cd","Continuous Delivery","icvr_title","ICVR","dockaboat_title","Dockaboat","qualitech_title","Qualitech","overup_title","OverUp","cyberlink_title","Cyberlink",n,"Independent","guazuapp_title","Guaz\xfaApp","ghp_title","GHP \u2014 CareCart","foxy_title","Foxy","icvr_years","2025 - Present","dockaboat_years","2024 - 2025","qualitech_years","2011 - 2013","overUp_years","2015 - 2017","cyberlink_years","2017 - 2018",m,"2018 - 2020","guazuapp_years","2021 - 2023","ghp_years","2023 - 2024","icvr_right_title","Pipeline Tools Developer for DCC Applications","dockaboat_right_title","Mobile Application Developer (Flutter)",l,"IT Solutions",k,"IT Solutions",j,"IT Company",i,"Independent Backend Engineer",h,"Multichannel Messaging Platform","ghp_right_title","Full-Stack Developer \u2014 CareCart Project","icvr_right_subtitle","Role: Pipeline tools developer focusing on Python automation and DCC integrations (Blender) for production environments.","dockaboat_right_subtitle","Role: Sole Flutter developer responsible for delivery, stabilization, and payments/subscriptions integration.",g,"Role: Network and systems technician.",f,"Role: Co-founder and software developer.",e,"Role: Technical support specialist.",d,"Role: Independent backend engineer delivering automation platforms and microservice-based systems for multiple clients.",c,"Role: Co-founder, full-stack engineer, and technical lead.",b,"Role: Lead mobile platform developer.","icvr_third_line","Website: https://ictools.io/","dockaboat_third_line","Website: https://dockaboat.app",a,"Website: https://qualitech.com.ar/",a0,"",a1,"Website: https://cyberlink.com.ar/",a2,"",a3,"Web app: %DOWN https://app.guazuapp.com.","ghp_third_line","Web app: https://carecart.com/","foxy_third_line",a4,"icvr_fourth_line","","dockaboat_fourth_line","",a5,"",a6,"",a7,"",a8,"",a9,"Android app:  %DOWN  https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ar.guazuapp.guazuapp","ghp_fourth_line","",b0,b1,"cnc_cad_title","CNCAD",b2,"Camera Switch QuickAccess",b3,"Entity Project API","guazuApp_title","GuazuaApp","myResume_title","My Personal Resume",b4,"Prototype Design Software, CNC Software Controller, and Router for Polyethylene Cutting",b5,"The project was developed to facilitate boarding maneuvers by providing fast access to the cameras on a vessel",b6,"Real-time Notifications and Task Creation A GraphQL API written in Python utilizing WebSockets for Push Messages",b7,"Multichannel messaging system",b8,"I am excited to share my work with the community and hope it will be useful for other developers","foxy_subtitle","Foxy is a cross-platform tool. It offers real-time web scraping, Optical Character Recognition (OCR), data labeling, and modeling, with export options to databases and spreadsheets.","cnc_cad_text","The decision to develop this project was driven by a desire to learn. Initiated in early 2013, it was completed in mid-2014 due to various reasons. The primary motivation behind the development of this project was to gain knowledge and experience in computer-programmed machining processes, independent of software and hardware already developed by third parties. In contrast to complex industrial CNC machines and software, this project provides a more basic perspective.\n\nThe objective of this project is to provide a foundational tool for students and individuals seeking to understand or venture into CNC machine processes.\n\nThe material, documentation, and experience gained from this project are intended to support and serve new ideas, whether for different purposes or not. Furthermore, individuals can use this prototype project as a basis to develop more elaborate and complex CNC systems.",b9,"In the source code repository there is a circuit schematic, 3D model (for Proteus) and the code for the microcontroller written in C. The system is 8-channel, includes a 16x2 LCD screen and a matrix keyboard. It is based on a PIC 18F4550 microcontroller, but can be downgraded to one with lower specs if needed.","entity_api_text","The project I'm describing is a software that provides a GraphQL-based API written in Python for task creation and tracking, as well as product requesting and real-time notifications to their recipients. The system communicates through WebSockets, allowing for efficient and real-time push messaging.\n\nUsers can interact with the system and receive real-time notifications about the status of their tasks and orders. Additionally, the API has been designed to be easily integrable into other applications and systems.","guazuApp_text","Guaz\xfaApp aimed to be a tool for communicating with your customers and within your organization. It was an ambitious project designed to integrate all your social media interactions into one place, redirecting customers to the right people within your organization.\n\nAdditionally, Guaz\xfaApp also intended to enhance internal communication.\n\nUnfortunately, the project has been canceled.","ghp_text","Gilson Software Solutions has been dedicated to providing software products that utilize the latest technology for housing markets.","foxy_text","It is composed of two main modules: Collector and Processor.\nThe Collector Module manages the capture process by allowing users to configure images that signal the start, optional captures during, and the end of a session. It also monitors specific areas for changes and automatically captures new images if changes are detected.\nThe Processor Module focuses on defining areas of interest within captured images, crucial for OCR and data extraction. It allows users to label areas, test extraction settings, and export processed data to databases or spreadsheets for further analysis.","myResume_text","This website has been developed using Dart/Flutter technology. The widget for the 'Skills' section was created from scratch to offer a personalized and engaging experience. Soon, this widget will be available in the official package repository (pub.dev).",c0,"Web Page",c1,"Source Code",c2,"Source Code",c3,"App Web",c4,"Source Code","foxy_name_link1","Site Web",c5,"Source Code",c6,"",c7,"",c8,"Google Play App",c9,"","ghp_name_link2","","foxy_name_link2","Source Code","show_more","Show more","show_less","Show less","send","SEND","clipboard","Copied to clipboard","contact_to_me","Get in touch!","required_field","This field is required",d0,"Your message is required!",d1,"Email address is incorrect format",d2,"An error occurred while sending the message.",d3,"The message was sent successfully","name","Name","phone","Phone"],s,s),"es_AR",A.aw(["about_me_title","Informaci\xf3n Personal","about","Sobre m\xed","profession","Senior Software Engineer \u2014 Backend en Python y Sistemas de Automatizaci\xf3n","about_me","Senior Software Engineer con m\xe1s de 12 a\xf1os de experiencia en desarrollo backend en Python, microservicios y sistemas de automatizaci\xf3n. Especializado en la construcci\xf3n de plataformas productivas y herramientas de workflow para entornos de Creaci\xf3n de Contenido Digital (DCC).",p,"Comenc\xe9 a programar en 2007 trabajando con microcontroladores PIC utilizando Assembler y C. Posteriormente realic\xe9 estudios terciarios en An\xe1lisis de Sistemas y Programaci\xf3n, fortaleciendo mis habilidades en Java y Python.\n\nCon el tiempo me especialic\xe9 en ingenier\xeda backend, enfoc\xe1ndome en microservicios en Python, dise\xf1o de APIs, frameworks de automatizaci\xf3n y sistemas de pipelines de producci\xf3n. Actualmente trabajo principalmente con Python para backend y Flutter para aplicaciones m\xf3viles seleccionadas, explorando continuamente nuevas tecnolog\xedas como Rust.",o,"A lo largo de mi carrera desarroll\xe9 s\xf3lidas habilidades de comunicaci\xf3n, resoluci\xf3n de problemas y trabajo en equipo. He desempe\xf1ado roles como empleado, emprendedor y l\xedder t\xe9cnico, lo que me permiti\xf3 fortalecer capacidades de liderazgo, resoluci\xf3n de conflictos y colaboraci\xf3n en entornos t\xe9cnicos complejos.","sysadmin_text","Mi experiencia en administraci\xf3n de sistemas comenz\xf3 en 2007 y se expandi\xf3 a trav\xe9s de trabajos profesionales configurando servidores, arreglos RAID e infraestructura de red. Con el tiempo adquir\xed experiencia pr\xe1ctica en Linux, Windows Server, virtualizaci\xf3n, redes, cl\xfasteres Kubernetes y servicios de Google Cloud.","full_stack_text","Me especializo en sistemas backend y automatizaci\xf3n, abordando arquitectura de aplicaciones, dise\xf1o de APIs, microservicios y flujos de despliegue en entornos productivos.","frontend_text","Me enfoco en construir interfaces eficientes y mantenibles, priorizando rendimiento, escalabilidad e integraci\xf3n limpia con sistemas backend.","backend_text","Mi principal fortaleza es la arquitectura backend, incluyendo microservicios en Python, dise\xf1o de bases de datos, APIs escalables y frameworks de automatizaci\xf3n productivos.","deployment_text","Dise\xf1o y gestiono flujos de despliegue con foco en seguridad, rendimiento, escalabilidad, monitoreo e integraci\xf3n y entrega continua.","electronic_text","Mi inter\xe9s por la electr\xf3nica comenz\xf3 en la infancia y luego se expandi\xf3 a sistemas embebidos, desarrollo CNC e integraci\xf3n hardware\u2013software usando microcontroladores y MicroPython.","_about_me","Sobre m\xed","_knowledge","Habilidades","_experience","Experiencia","_projects","Proyectos","_contact","Contacto","languages","Lenguajes","queryLanguages","Lenguajes de consulta","paradigms","Paradigmas","objectOriented","Orientado a Objetos","concurrent","Concurrente","reactive","Reactivo","parallel","Paralelo","functional","Funcional","declarative","Declarativo","serviceOriented","Orientado a Servicios","qualitech_title","Qualitech","overup_title","OverUp","cyberlink_title","Cyberlink",n,"Independiente","guazuapp_title","Guaz\xfaApp","ghp_title","Gilson Housing Partners","qualitech_years","2011 - 2013","overUp_years","2015 - 2017","cyberlink_years","2017 - 2018",m,"2018 - 2020","guazuapp_years","2021 - 2023","ghp_years","2023 - 2024",l,"Soluciones IT",k,"Soluciones IT",j,"Empresa de IT",i,"Ingeniero Backend Independiente",h,"Plataforma de mensajer\xeda multicanal","ghp_right_title","Desarrollador Full Stack \u2014 Proyecto CareCart",g,d4,f,"Rol: Cofundador y desarrollador de software.",e,"Rol: Especialista en soporte t\xe9cnico.",d,"",c,"Rol: Cofundador, ingeniero full stack y l\xedder t\xe9cnico.",b,"Rol: Desarrollador l\xedder de plataforma mobile.",g,d4,f,"Rol: Socio fundador, desarrollador de software y, eventualmente, en el \xe1rea de electr\xf3nica.",e,"Rol: T\xe9cnico general en el \xe1rea de soporte.",d,"",c,"Rol: Socio fundador, desarrollador full stack y l\xedder de desarrollo.",b,"Desarrollador Full Stack y L\xedder de Proyecto en CareCart","foxy_right_subtitle","Rol: Desarrollador Fundador",a,"P\xe1gina web: https://qualitech.com.ar/",a0,"",a1,"P\xe1gina web: https://cyberlink.com.ar/",a2,"",a3,"Aplicaci\xf3n web: %DOWN https://app.guazuapp.com.","ghp_third_line","Aplicaci\xf3n web: https://carecart.com/","foxy_third_line",a4,a5,"",a6,"",a7,"",a8,"",a9,"Aplicaci\xf3n para Android: %DOWN https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ar.guazuapp.guazuapp","ghp_fourth_line","",b0,b1,"cnc_cad_title","CNCAD",b2,"Conmutador de Camara, QuickAccess",b3,"Entity API","guazuApp_title","GuazuaApp","myResume_title","Mi Curr\xedculum Personal",b4,"Software de dise\xf1o de prototipos, controlador de software CNC y enrutador para corte de polietileno",b5,"El proyecto fue desarrollado para facilitar las maniobras de abordaje al proporcionar un acceso r\xe1pido a las c\xe1maras en una embarcaci\xf3n.",b6,"Notificaciones en tiempo real y creaci\xf3n de tareas Una API GraphQL escrita en Python que utiliza WebSockets para mensajes push",b7,"Sistema de mensajer\xeda multicanal",b8,"Estoy emocionado de compartir mi trabajo con la comunidad y espero que sea \xfatil para otros desarrolladores.","foxy_subtitle","Foxy es una herramienta multiplataforma que soporta Linux, Windows y macOS. Ofrece scraping web en tiempo real, Reconocimiento \xd3ptico de Caracteres (OCR), etiquetado y modelado de datos, con opciones de exportaci\xf3n a bases de datos y hojas de c\xe1lculo.","cnc_cad_text","La decisi\xf3n de desarrollar este proyecto fue impulsada por el deseo de aprender. Iniciado a principios de 2013, se complet\xf3 a mediados de 2014 por diversas razones. La principal motivaci\xf3n detr\xe1s del desarrollo de este proyecto fue ganar conocimiento y experiencia en procesos de maquinado programados por computadora, independientes del software y hardware ya desarrollado por terceros. A diferencia de las complejas m\xe1quinas CNC industriales y el software, este proyecto ofrece una perspectiva m\xe1s b\xe1sica.\n\nEl objetivo de este proyecto es proporcionar una herramienta fundamental para estudiantes e individuos que buscan comprender o aventurarse en los procesos de m\xe1quinas CNC.\n\nEl material, la documentaci\xf3n y la experiencia obtenida de este proyecto est\xe1n destinados a respaldar y servir nuevas ideas, ya sea para diferentes prop\xf3sitos o no. Adem\xe1s, las personas pueden utilizar este proyecto prototipo como base para desarrollar sistemas CNC m\xe1s elaborados y complejos.",b9,"En el repositorio del codigo fuente se encuentra esquema de circuito, modelo 3D (para Proteus) y el c\xf3digo para el microcontrolador escrito en C, El sistema es de 8 canales, incluye una pantalla LCD 16x2 y un teclado de matriz. Se basa en un microcontrolador PIC 18F4550, pero puede ser reemplazado por uno que tenga especificaciones m\xe1s bajas si es necesario.","entity_api_text","El proyecto es un software que proporciona una API basada en GraphQL escrita en Python para la creaci\xf3n y seguimiento de tareas, as\xed como la solicitud de productos y notificaciones en tiempo real a sus destinatarios. El sistema se comunica a trav\xe9s de WebSockets, lo que permite una mensajer\xeda push eficiente y en tiempo real.\n\n Los usuarios pueden interactuar con el sistema y recibir notificaciones en tiempo real sobre el estado de sus tareas y pedidos. Adem\xe1s, la API ha sido dise\xf1ada para ser f\xe1cilmente integrable en otras aplicaciones y sistemas.","guazuApp_text","Era un proyecto ambicioso dise\xf1ado para integrar todas tus interacciones en redes sociales en un solo lugar, redirigiendo a los clientes a las personas adecuadas dentro de tu organizaci\xf3n.\n\nAdem\xe1s, Guaz\xfaApp tambi\xe9n ten\xeda como objetivo mejorar la comunicaci\xf3n interna.\n\nLamentablemente, el proyecto ha sido cancelado.","myResume_text","Este sitio web ha sido desarrollado utilizando la tecnolog\xeda de Dart/Flutter. El widget de la secci\xf3n 'Habilidades' fue creado desde cero para ofrecer una experiencia personalizada y atractiva. Pronto, este widget estar\xe1 disponible en el repositorio oficial de paquetes (pub.dev).","ghp_text","Gilson Software Solutions se ha dedicado a proporcionar productos de software que utilizan la \xfaltima tecnolog\xeda para mercados inmobiliarios.","foxy_text","Est\xe1 compuesto por dos m\xf3dulos principales: Colector y Procesador.\nEl M\xf3dulo Colector gestiona el proceso de captura permitiendo a los usuarios configurar im\xe1genes que indiquen el inicio, capturas opcionales durante la sesi\xf3n y el final de la misma. Tambi\xe9n monitorea \xe1reas espec\xedficas en busca de cambios y captura nuevas im\xe1genes autom\xe1ticamente si se detectan cambios.\nEl M\xf3dulo Procesador se enfoca en definir \xe1reas de inter\xe9s dentro de las im\xe1genes capturadas, lo cual es crucial para OCR y la extracci\xf3n de datos. Permite a los usuarios etiquetar \xe1reas, probar configuraciones de extracci\xf3n y exportar los datos procesados a bases de datos o hojas de c\xe1lculo para su an\xe1lisis posterior.",c0,"P\xe1gina Web",c1,"C\xf3digo Fuente",c2,"C\xf3digo Fuente",c3,"App Web",c4,"C\xf3digo Fuente","foxy_name_link1","P\xe1gina Web",c5,"C\xf3digo Fuente",c6,"",c7,"","ghp_name_link2","","foxy_name_link2","Source Code",c8,"Google PLay App",c9,"","show_more","Mostrar m\xe1s","show_less","Mostrar menos","send","ENVIAR","clipboard","Copiado al portapales","contact_to_me","\xa1Cont\xe1ctame!","required_field","Este campo es necesario.",d0,"T\xfa mensaje es requerido!",d1,"La direcci\xf3n de correo electr\xf3nico tiene un formato incorrecto.",d2,"Se produjo un error al enviar el mensaje.",d3,"El mensaje fue enviado con \xe9xito.","name","* Nombre","phone","Tel\xe9fono"],s,s)],s,t.GU))
